title: [Boreas Hills, Etesian Terrace]
description: The ground slopes upwards a bit towards the north here, as two rows of currant bushes line a street leading off the main road.  Small paths wind their way from the road to the doors of several well-kept houses.

The ground slopes upwards a bit towards the north here, as two rows of currant bushes line a street leading off the main road.  Small paths wind their way from the road to several well-kept houses, lit lamps hanging next to their doors.
